{"id":23691,"date":"2024-02-22T18:23:53","date_gmt":"2021-07-22T12:53:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=23691"},"modified":"2024-11-19T17:17:54","modified_gmt":"2024-11-19T11:47:54","slug":"glass-door-designs-for-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/glass-door-designs-for-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Glass Door Designs For Bedroom That Are Clear Winners"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Glass doors for and within the bedroom can be both beautiful and space-saving<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedrooms are one of the most private spaces in your home, which is why a glass bedroom door isn\u2019t an option that you would naturally think of for the space. But some instances require you to think of an alternative solution to the more solid door options like wood for the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-door-designs-for-home\/\">bedroom door<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are some of the reasons why you should consider getting glass(es) for your bedroom?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Glass bedroom doors create the illusion of more space.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They bring in more light and overall brightness to the bedroom.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Glass door designs for bedrooms (the sliding kind) help save space in smaller bedrooms.\u00a0<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>They make for a sleek and stylish addition to the house.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are seven glass door designs for the bedroom that work equally well as traditional doors.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sleek Glass Bedroom Door Looks Super Stylish<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern studio is the quintessential bachelor\u2019s pad with its sleek and minimal design. The glass door greatly helps in maintaining the look of this space. Apt for areas where maintaining the privacy element for the bedroom isn\u2019t the biggest concern, this glass door is an excellent substitute to a bedroom door in solid materials.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180341\/sleek-glass-bedroom-door-looks-super-stylish.jpg\" alt=\"Sleek glass door design for bedroom where privacy isn't the biggest concern\" class=\"wp-image-23700\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180341\/sleek-glass-bedroom-door-looks-super-stylish.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180341\/sleek-glass-bedroom-door-looks-super-stylish-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180341\/sleek-glass-bedroom-door-looks-super-stylish-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180341\/sleek-glass-bedroom-door-looks-super-stylish-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The glass door does all the right things for this modern apartment bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Glass Bedroom Door Is Apt For Studio Apartments<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A solid wall between the living room and the bedroom in this studio apartment would have taken away the beauty and charm of the space. The glass door \u2014 and even the glass partition for this bedroom \u2014 helps open up the studio apartment to a great extent. Since <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/studio-apartment-interior-design-ideas\/\">studio apartments<\/a> are meant for one person to live in, the lack of privacy isn\u2019t a cause of significant concern.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180304\/bedroom-with-glass-door-for-studio-apartments.jpg\" alt=\"A glass bedroom door design for a studio apartment is a space saving option\" class=\"wp-image-23694\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180304\/bedroom-with-glass-door-for-studio-apartments.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180304\/bedroom-with-glass-door-for-studio-apartments-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180304\/bedroom-with-glass-door-for-studio-apartments-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180304\/bedroom-with-glass-door-for-studio-apartments-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Studio apartments need all hands on deck when it comes to space-saving options<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go For Glass Bedroom Door That Opens Up To The Bathroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are keen on adding a glass door element to the bedroom without taking away the complete privacy element, a glass door for the attached bathroom is an option. The glass door-cum-partition between these two spaces brightens the entire room and makes it seem more open and spacious. The clear glass giving a peek into the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/luxury-bathroom-design\/\">luxurious bathroom<\/a> makes the overall space look incredibly stylish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180310\/bedroom-with-sliding-glass-door-that-opens-up-to-bathroom.jpg\" alt=\"Glass bedroom door design that opens up to the bathroom\" class=\"wp-image-23695\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180310\/bedroom-with-sliding-glass-door-that-opens-up-to-bathroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180310\/bedroom-with-sliding-glass-door-that-opens-up-to-bathroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180310\/bedroom-with-sliding-glass-door-that-opens-up-to-bathroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180310\/bedroom-with-sliding-glass-door-that-opens-up-to-bathroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">It doesn\u2019t get better than a glass door-cum-partition for an attached bathroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Glass Bedroom Door That Opens Up To The Dressing Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A large bedroom deserves to have its own walk-in closet or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/latest-dressing-room-design-ideas\/\">dressing room<\/a>. You can consider having sliding glass doors for the entrance to the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">walk-in closet<\/a>. This way, the entire area of the bedroom still remains together and more open from a visual point of view.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180317\/glass-bedroom-door-that-opens-up-to-the-dressing-room.jpg\" alt=\"Glass bedroom door design that opens up to dressing room or walk-in-closet\" class=\"wp-image-23696\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180317\/glass-bedroom-door-that-opens-up-to-the-dressing-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180317\/glass-bedroom-door-that-opens-up-to-the-dressing-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180317\/glass-bedroom-door-that-opens-up-to-the-dressing-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180317\/glass-bedroom-door-that-opens-up-to-the-dressing-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Glass doors are an option for spacious bedrooms too<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Collapsible Glass Bedroom Door For A Modern Apartment<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A collapsible glass door design comes in handy when you don\u2019t want the walls to be up 24X7 in a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/studio-apartment-interior-design-ideas\/\">modern studio apartment<\/a>. The glass doors for the bedroom are a great substitute for actual walls to create a partition between the bedroom and the living room. Due to the design of the glass doors, you always have the option of keeping the door open and making the total space look more spacious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180335\/modern-bedroom-door-design-with-glass.jpg\" alt=\"Collapsible glass bedroom door design  for apartments with space constraints\" class=\"wp-image-23699\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180335\/modern-bedroom-door-design-with-glass.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180335\/modern-bedroom-door-design-with-glass-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180335\/modern-bedroom-door-design-with-glass-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180335\/modern-bedroom-door-design-with-glass-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Collapsible glass door designs are a boon for small apartments with space constraints<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sturdy Glass Bedroom Doors Are A Perfect Gateway To The Balcony<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most modern homes have attached balconies or terraces that come with glass doors. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-glass-door-designs\/\">Sliding glass doors<\/a>, or even <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/glass-door-designs-for-bedroom\/\">regular glass doors for the bedroom<\/a> that open up to the balcony, help get a little bit of the outdoors inside. As with any glass door, it is essential to verify the sturdiness of the glass used to create such a door.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180347\/sliding-glass-door-design-for-bedroom-gateway-to-balcony.jpg\" alt=\"Minimal sliding glass door design for bedroom balcony that brings in more natural lights.\" class=\"wp-image-23701\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180347\/sliding-glass-door-design-for-bedroom-gateway-to-balcony.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180347\/sliding-glass-door-design-for-bedroom-gateway-to-balcony-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180347\/sliding-glass-door-design-for-bedroom-gateway-to-balcony-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180347\/sliding-glass-door-design-for-bedroom-gateway-to-balcony-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Glass doors for the bedroom balcony means more natural light<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Glass Doors Are Apt For Small Bedrooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a small bedroom? Small, makeshift spaces either have a space crunch or insufficient lighting. Consider getting a glass door to brighten it up. Regular glass doors help make the area look brighter, whereas a small bedroom with sliding glass doors helps save space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180323\/glass-door-design-for-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Glass door design for small bedroom, that brighten up the whole space\" class=\"wp-image-23697\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180323\/glass-door-design-for-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180323\/glass-door-design-for-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180323\/glass-door-design-for-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/22180323\/glass-door-design-for-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Glass doors are an excellent fit for small bedrooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The most important thing to consider while going for a bedroom glass door is the type of glass used&nbsp; \u2014 from an aesthetic, functional, and safety perspective. Second, you don\u2019t have to entirely give up on the privacy element just because you are opting for glass doors. Curtains and blinds can help you with the privacy setting as and when required.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are your thoughts on going for glass door designs for bedrooms?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, more about <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-door-designs-for-home\/\">Modern Bedroom Door Designs For Home<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/fluted-glass-door-ideas\/\">Reasons to Choose Fluted Glass Doors for Your Home<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=